title: Championship Round Red Challenge Flag Picks & whose legacy changes with a SB LIV win?
itunes:title: Championship Round Red Challenge Flag Picks & whose legacy changes with a SB LIV win?
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in Studio 66 by Matt "Money" Smith to get you ready for Championship weekend! Money starts off with reading some of Eddie Spaghetti's latest Tweets (3:18). Then, Shek asks if Lamar Jackson was a victim of the curse of "s'posta" (8:18)? Next, the guys debated whose legacy changes the most with a Super Bowl win in Miami (24:45). Lastly, the group rounds out the show by making their Red Challenge Flag picks for the Titans vs Chiefs and the Packers vs 49ers (38:02).
